{"word":"G511 - ἀνώτερος - anṓteros - an-o'-ter-os - Above","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνώτερος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anṓteros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-o'-ter-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Above</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective Neuter / பெயரடை (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"உயர்ந்த, மேல் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"higher"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Comparative degree of <a href=\"#/G507 - ἄνω - ánō - an'-o/507\">G507</a>; <i>upper</i>, that is, (neuter as adverb) to a <i>more conspicuous</i> place, in a <i>former</i> part of the book: - above, higher.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G507/507\">G507</a>, <a href=\"#/G509/509\">G509</a>, <a href=\"#/G511/511\">G511</a>"}]}